Package: mathGen
Type: Package
Title: Scraping and Visualizing Relationships from the Math Genealogy Project
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2015-11-06
Author: Heike Hofmann
Maintainer: Heike Hofmann <hofmann@iastate.edu>
Description: The Mathematics Genealogy Project is a database compiling information on mathematicians (and statisticians) all over the world, keeping track of academic doctoral relations. It is a service of the NDSU Department of Mathematics, in association with the American Mathematical Society. We are scraping the available websites and provide visualizations of the academic relationships.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://github.com/heike/mathGen
BugReports: https://github.com/heike/mathGen/issues
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14)
Imports:
  XML,
  httr,
  plyr
Suggests:
  ggplot2 (>= 1.0.1.9003),
  geomnet
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
